/*
this is a simple hello world proram, but just demonstrates
using and declaring functions. Also demonstrates one of the
more verbose loops.
*/

// call the function we define later. We will make it print "hello world" 4 times
helloFunction("world" 4)

//the actual definition of the function
helloFunction(noun times):
{
	for({=(1 0)} {<(i times)} {=(i +(i 1))})
	{
		printsp("hello" noun)
	}
}